<p><span class="vocab">三時間目<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>三時間目</rb><rt>さんじかんめ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;third hour</span></span>も、<span class="vocab">四時間目<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>四時間目</rb><rt>よじかんめ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;fourth hour</span></span>も<span class="vocab">昼過ぎ<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>昼過</rb><rt>ひるす</rt></ruby>ぎ&nbsp;afternoon</span></span>の<span class="vocab">一時間<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>一時間</rb><rt>いちじかん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;hour</span></span>も<span class="vocab">大同小異<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>大同小異</rb><rt>だいどうしょうい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;generally the same</span></span>であった。<span class="vocab">最初の<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>最初</rb><rt>さいしょ</rt></ruby>の&nbsp;the first</span></span><span class="vocab">日<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>日</rb><rt>ひ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;day</span></span>に<span class="vocab">出た<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>出</rb><rt>で</rt></ruby>た&nbsp;made an appearance</span></span><span class="vocab">級<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>級</rb><rt>くみ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;classes</span></span>は、いずれも<span class="vocab">少々<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>少々</rb><rt>しょうしょう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;a little bit</span></span>ずつ<span class="vocab">失敗した<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>失敗</rb><rt>しっぱい</rt></ruby>した&nbsp;made a mistake; experienced failure</span></span>。<span class="vocab">教師<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>教師</rb><rt>きょうし</rt></ruby>&nbsp;instructor</span></span>は<span class="vocab">はたで見るほど<span class="vocabdef">はたで<ruby><rb>見</rb><rt>み</rt></ruby>るほど&nbsp;as it seems from a distance</span></span><span class="vocab">楽<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>楽</rb><rt>らく</rt></ruby>&nbsp;easy</span></span>じゃないと<span class="vocab">思った<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>思</rb><rt>おも</rt></ruby>った&nbsp;thought; realized</span></span>。<span class="vocab">授業<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>授業</rb><rt>じゅぎょう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;lessons</span></span>は<span class="vocab">ひと通り<span class="vocabdef">ひと<ruby><rb>通</rb><rt>とお</rt></ruby>り&nbsp;in a general way; respectably enough</span></span><span class="vocab">済んだ<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>済</rb><rt>す</rt></ruby>んだ&nbsp;finished; were concluded</span></span>が、まだ<span class="vocab">帰れない<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>帰</rb><rt>かえ</rt></ruby>れない&nbsp;cannot go home</span></span>、<span class="vocab">三時<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>三時</rb><rt>さんじ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;three o'clock</span></span>まで<span class="vocab">ぽつ然として<span class="vocabdef">ぽつ<ruby><rb>然</rb><rt>ねん</rt></ruby>として&nbsp;vacantly; absent-mindedly</span></span><span class="vocab">待ってなくてはならん<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>待</rb><rt>ま</rt></ruby>ってなくてはならん&nbsp;must wait</span></span>。三時になると、<span class="vocab">受持<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>受持</rb><rt>うけもち</rt></ruby>&nbsp;under one's charge</span></span>級の<span class="vocab">生徒<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>生徒</rb><rt>せいと</rt></ruby>&nbsp;students</span></span>が<span class="vocab">自分<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>自分</rb><rt>じぶん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;(their) own</span></span>の<span class="vocab">教室<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>教室</rb><rt>きょうしつ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;classroom</span></span>を<span class="vocab">掃除して<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>掃除</rb><rt>そうじ</rt></ruby>して&nbsp;clean</span></span><span class="vocab">報知<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>報知</rb><rt>しらせ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;notification</span></span>にくるから<span class="vocab">検分<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>検分</rb><rt>けんぶん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;inspection</span></span>をするんだそうだ。それから、<span class="vocab">出席簿<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>出席簿</rb><rt>しゅっせきぼ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;attendance list</span></span>を<span class="vocab">一応<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>一応</rb><rt>いちおう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;once</span></span><span class="vocab">調べて<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>調</rb><rt>しら</rt></ruby>べて&nbsp;check</span></span>ようやく<span class="vocab">お暇<span class="vocabdef">お<ruby><rb>暇</rb><rt>ひま</rt></ruby>&nbsp;leisure (hours)</span></span>が<span class="vocab">出る<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>出</rb><rt>で</rt></ruby>る&nbsp;present itself</span></span>。いくら<span class="vocab">月給<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>月給</rb><rt>げっきゅう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;salary</span></span>で<span class="vocab">買われた<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>買</rb><rt>か</rt></ruby>われた&nbsp;be bought; be purchased</span></span><span class="vocab">身体<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>身体</rb><rt>からだ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;body</span></span>だって、あいた<span class="vocab">時間<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>時間</rb><rt>じかん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;time</span></span>まで<span class="vocab">学校<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>学校</rb><rt>がっこう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;school</span></span>へ<span class="vocab">縛りつけて<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>縛</rb><rt>しば</rt></ruby>りつけて&nbsp;tied to</span></span><span class="vocab">机<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>机</rb><rt>つくえ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;desk</span></span>と<span class="vocab">睨めっくら<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>睨</rb><rt>にら</rt></ruby>めっくら&nbsp;stare-down</span></span>をさせるなんて<span class="vocab">法がある<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>法</rb><rt>ほう</rt></ruby>がある&nbsp;to be reasonable</span></span>ものか。しかし<span class="vocab">ほかの連中<span class="vocabdef">ほかの<ruby><rb>連中</rb><rt>れんちゅう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;rest of the company; everyone else</span></span>はみんな<span class="vocab">大人しく<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>大人</rb><rt>おとな</rt></ruby>しく&nbsp;obediently</span></span><span class="vocab">ご規則通り<span class="vocabdef">ご<ruby><rb>規則通</rb><rt>きそくどお</rt></ruby>り&nbsp;adhering to the rules</span></span>やってるから<span class="vocab">新参<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>新参</rb><rt>しんざん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;newcomer</span></span>のおればかり、<span class="vocab">だだを捏ねる<span class="vocabdef">だだを<ruby><rb>捏</rb><rt>こ</rt></ruby>ねる&nbsp;make a fuss (about something)</span></span>のもよろしくないと思って<span class="vocab">我慢<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>我慢</rb><rt>がまん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;patience; sufferance</span></span>していた。<span class="vocab">帰りがけ<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>帰</rb><rt>かえ</rt></ruby>りがけ&nbsp;on the way back</span></span>に、<span class="vocab">君<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>君</rb><rt>きみ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;you; hey</span></span><span class="vocab">何でもかんでも<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>何</rb><rt>なん</rt></ruby>でもかんでも&nbsp;no matter what; regardless of circumstances</span></span><span class="vocab">三時過<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>三時過</rb><rt>さんじすぎ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;after three o'clock</span></span>まで<span class="vocab">学校<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>学校</rb><rt>がっこう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;school</span></span>にいさせるのは<span class="vocab">愚<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>愚</rb><rt>おろか</rt></ruby>&nbsp;foolish; asinine</span></span>だぜと<span class="vocab">山嵐<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>山嵐</rb><rt>やまあらし</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Yama Arashi (nickname for Hotta, the head mathematics teacher)</span></span>に<span class="vocab">訴えたら<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>訴</rb><rt>うった</rt></ruby>えたら&nbsp;complained</span></span>、山嵐はそうさアハハハと<span class="vocab">笑った<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>笑</rb><rt>わら</rt></ruby>った&nbsp;laughed</span></span>が、あとから<span class="vocab">真面目<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>真面目</rb><rt>まじめ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;serious</span></span>になって、君あまり学校の<span class="vocab">不平<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>不平</rb><rt>ふへい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;discontent; grievance</span></span>を<span class="vocab">云う<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>云</rb><rt>い</rt></ruby>う&nbsp;say; mention</span></span>と、いかんぜ。云うなら<span class="vocab">僕<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>僕</rb><rt>ぼく</rt></ruby>&nbsp;me</span></span>だけに<span class="vocab">話せ<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>話</rb><rt>はな</rt></ruby>せ&nbsp;tell; talk to</span></span>、<span class="vocab">随分<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>随分</rb><rt>ずいぶん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;very much</span></span><span class="vocab">妙な<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>妙</rb><rt>みょう</rt></ruby>な&nbsp;strange; odd</span></span><span class="vocab">人<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>人</rb><rt>ひと</rt></ruby>&nbsp;people</span></span>も<span class="vocab">居る<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>居</rb><rt>い</rt></ruby>る&nbsp;to be</span></span>からなと<span class="vocab">忠告<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>忠告</rb><rt>ちゅうこく</rt></ruby>&nbsp;warning; caution</span></span><span class="vocab">がましい<span class="vocabdef">がましい&nbsp;sounding like (suffix)</span></span><span class="vocab">事<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>事</rb><rt>こと</rt></ruby>&nbsp;act; fact</span></span>を云った。<span class="vocab">四つ角<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>四</rb><rt>よ</rt></ruby>つ<ruby><rb>角</rb><rt>かど</rt></ruby>&nbsp;corner; intersection</span></span>で<span class="vocab">分れた<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>分</rb><rt>わか</rt></ruby>れた&nbsp;parted (ways)</span></span>から<span class="vocab">詳しい<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>詳</rb><rt>くわ</rt></ruby>しい&nbsp;detailed</span></span>事は<span class="vocab">聞く<span class="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>聞</rb><rt>き</rt></ruby>く&nbsp;ask</span></span>ひまがなかった。</p>

